{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p}} – [[spawn]], [[egg]].

===Etymology 1===
Usually thought of as derived from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*sV-row||egg, nit}} with nominalizing suffix {{m|und|*‑n}}; compare {{cog|bo|སྲོ་མ||egg of a louse, nit, small bubble}} ({{zh-ref|Benedict, 1976}}; {{zh-ref|Gong, 1995}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}; STEDT).

Alternatively, STEDT compares it to {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*(r/l)um||egg}}, while noting a few phonological problems with the comparison.

{{zh-ref|Sagart and Ma (2020)}} propose that it may be related to {{och-l|果|fruit}}.

